<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= department.name %> - Details</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .navbar {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #333;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .navbar a {
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .navbar a:hover {
            background-color: #555;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .content h1 {
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="navbar">
    <a href="#programme">Programme</a>
    <a href="#faculties">Faculties</a>
    <a href="#labs">Labs</a>
</div>

<div class="content">
    <h1>Welcome to the <%= department.name %> Department</h1>
    <p>Here you can find information about the department's programme, faculties, and labs.</p>

    <section id="programme">
        <h2>Programme</h2>
        <p>Details about the programmes offered by the department.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="faculties">
        <h2>Faculties</h2>
        <p>Information about the faculties in this department.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="labs">
        <h2>Labs</h2>
        <p>Details about the labs and research facilities available in the department.</p>
    </section>
</div>

</body>
</html>
